<subpara id="RM00000276C000X_07" type-id="51" category="05" proc-id="RM0250U___00008QU00000">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<list1 type="nonmark">
<item>
<ptxt>If different DTCs that are related to a different system are output simultaneously while terminal E2 is used as a ground terminal, terminal E2 may be open.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM00000276C000X_08" type-id="01" category="01">
<name>PROCEDURE</name>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___00008QW00000">
<testtitle>CHECK HARNESS AND CONNECTOR (ECM - IMRV)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the C33 IMRV connector.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A136168E01" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the C24 ECM connector.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance between the terminals of the wire harness side connectors.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance (Check for open)</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-1 (IACA) - C24-93 (IACA)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-2 (EIA) - C24-126 (EIA)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-3 (VCIA) - C24-103 (VCIA)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance (Check for short)</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-1 (IACA) or C24-93 (IACA) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or more</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-3 (VCIA) or C24-103 (VCIA) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or more</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Reconnect the connectors.</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0003" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0007" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00008QX00000">
<testtitle>INSPECT ECM (VC VOLTAGE)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the C33 IMRV connector.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A132311E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to the ON position.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the voltage.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard voltage</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-1 (VCIA) - C33-2 (EIA)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>4.5 to 5.5 V</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0004" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0008" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0004">
<testtitle>REPLACE INTAKE MANIFOLD RUNNER VALVE ASSEMBLY</testtitle>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0005" fin="false">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0005" proc-id="RM0250U___00008QY00000">
<testtitle>CHECK WHETHER DTC OUTPUT RECURS</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Clear the DTC (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000PDK01MX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Start the engine.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Run the engine at more than 3,000 rpm.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>As running the engine to 3,000 rpm, the IMRV usually becomes fully opened. If the ignition switch is turned off under this condition, the IMRV is fully closed and then becomes half-opening angle.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch to the ON position 20 seconds later.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Read the DTCs.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Display (DTC output)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>P2014, P2016 and/or P2017 are output again</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>No DTC output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0006" fin="true">A</down>
<right ref="RM00000276C000X_08_0009" fin="true">B</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0006">
<testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0007">
<testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACE HARNESS OR CONNECTOR</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0008">
<testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276C000X_08_0009">
<testtitle>SYSTEM OK</testtitle>
</testgrp>
</subpara>
</para>
